</table></p>
<p>
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td><span><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200804/76c9af08612642a3849b4c6d7ad879aa.jpeg" /></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><span>巴特尔与队员们在灭火。</span><span>丁根厚摄（人民视觉）</span></td>
</tr>
